query:
SELECT i.id as inspection_id, i.vesselTagNumber, pr.id as report_id, cc.componentName, cc.componentType 
FROM inspections i 
LEFT JOIN professionalReports pr ON pr.inspectionId = i.id 
LEFT JOIN componentCalculations cc ON cc.reportId = pr.id 
WHERE i.vesselTagNumber = '54-11-001' 
ORDER BY i.createdAt DESC 
LIMIT 20
